description: Soul food has hit the streets of SoCal, and it's ready to show you what real Southern eating is like. This is Not Your Mamas Kitchen, and they're here to bring real flavor to the streets of Los Angeles. You've never had fried fish, chicken, fries, or anything else as satisfying as what these chefs are making for you. We just know that this truck will have you coming back again and again, even if it's only because you keep emptying your plate before you reach your table!
name: Not Your Mama's Kitchen
